text: Tatjana Ždanoka (, Tatyana Arkadyevna Zhdanok, born May 8, 1950) is a Latvian politician. She is a Member of the European Parliament for Latvia since 2019. She is co-chairwoman of the Latvian Russian Union. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Riga Category:MEPs for Latvia Category:Mathematicians
